nodes.text: Dorzek Senn was an alien who hosted a broadcast of a droid battle from the settlement of Galma on the planet Batuu. Senn co-hosted the broadcast with Blom Groffitch and Haz Bakkel, and it was played on radio station BSO 401.72 in Black Spire Outpost on Batuu during the war between the First Order and the Resistance.
Dorzek Senn was first created for Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge, which opened to guests at Disneyland Park on May 31, 2019.
